Canonical architectural direction

The review must evaluate the codebase against the now-established design model:

extent_identity
+
dictionary-based path resolution
+
mirrored dictionary copies (header + tail)
+
fail-closed naming semantics
+
anonymous fallback when naming proof is unavailable

Research variants should no longer influence canonical runtime logic.

